    "passives": {
      "TimeBreakerPassiveARoundTableKnightDark": {
        "id": "TimeBreakerPassiveARoundTableKnightDark",
        "found": true,
        "localization": {
          "name": "Steady Aim",
          "description": "This unit cannot fall asleep if there are any Water enemies on the battlefield. Each time a poisoned enemy gets the turn, this unit heals for 20% of its max HP.\n\nIf this unit would be defeated by an enemy attack or a status effect while having more than 1 HP, it instead survives with 1 HP.\n\nIf this unit damages at least one enemy with 100+TU with an attack, this unit will get another turn. Damaged targets cannot trigger this effect again until TU advances. Effects that influence TU order may interrupt the extra turn (e.g. Stuns targeting the lowest TU target)."
        }
      },
      "MegaGetTurnPassiveARoundTableKnightDark": {
        "id": "MegaGetTurnPassiveARoundTableKnightDark",
        "found": true,
        "localization": {
          "name": "Unholy Counter",
          "description": "When this unit gets a turn, it heals 50% of its max HP.\n\nThe first time this unit takes damage from an attack and survives until after the end of the turn while on the battlefield, this unit will enter Unholy Trance for 30TU plus 30TU per Awakening (up to 150TU if this unit has 4 Awakenings). While in Unholy Trance, this unit cannot be defeated by damage, and cannot be Stunned.\n\nWhen this unit takes damage from an attack, they will immediately get the next turn, this cannot trigger again until TU advances. Enemy units that deal damage to this unit get stunned for 100TU and Super Poisoned. These are Skin effects. This unit cannot become a Guardian or Stun Absorber."
        }
      },
